{
  "stem": "14060.8",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they examined you or they looked at you-- they didn't examine you-- and they said, yes or no.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You have to stay in the block or you go into hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had no idea of this-- of what went on in Block 61, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother was at least in as healthy, if not better condition, than I was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't take me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Immediately after the liberation, I became aware of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I read the records, which all sorts of false reasons were given-- pneumonia, dysentery, heart attack, whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It is a known fact it was conducted by a Polish non-Jew doctor who was giving all these injections, whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And whoever went there never came out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was literally-- look, on the camp records, which I have got, which I got from the Yad Vashem, it's written on it 'died, verstorben, 26 of March at 3:15 in the afternoon.' And that exactly, 15:15.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the camp was liberated on the 11th of April.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you can see how close we were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And nothing major has happened except the day before the liberation-- and I must tell you that, because that is really personal.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It happened to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A day before the liberation, on the 10th of April, the Germans instructed the German political inmates to form a human wall from the bottom camp, to the zeltlager all the way up to the appellplatz, and chase all the Jews-- because the Jews were more or less concentrated in the bottom lager and a little bit in the middle lager, not hardly any on the top lager-- and chase them out of the camp to have an appell and out.",
      "word_count": 81
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I felt it was getting very close.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
